1. create DWP
2. import external jars
3. need web.xml
4. add <servlet> for Dispatcher Servlet
5. add springs.xml
6.we don't have to write Hibernate.xml
7.For working with hibernate we need SessionFactory obj.
8.spring will create the obj for SessionFactory.
9.we need to write a bean tag for SessionFactory.
10.For SessionFactory dependency is the data Sources.
11.we need to write a bean tag for the data source.
12.For data source you have to specify driver class name,url,password.
13.And for SessionFactory we need to mention the hibernate properties.

